    filter=\(dqurl(#drop\-shadow\-filter)\(dq />
</\f[B]svg\f[R]>

\f[I]<!\-\- Button to update the shadow \-\->\f[R]
<\f[B]button\f[R] id=\(dqupdateShadow\(dq type=\(dqbutton\(dq>Update Shadow</\f[B]button\f[R]>
.EE
